1
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,530
It's fine if the Empress

2
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,240
doesn't come to the banquet,

3
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:52,020
but I didn't expect His Majesty to be absent too.

4
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,520
Prince Qi.

5
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,360
Didn't we agree that after that night,

6
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,420
we wouldn't meet in private anymore?

7
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,160
I heard

8
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:11,920
the Empress went to Chang'an Hall to see His Majesty this afternoon.

9
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:14,380
And tonight, they are both absent together.

10
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:17,160
When did they become so in sync?

11
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,160
It's just a coincidence.

12
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,560
As long as I'm here,

13
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:25,480
their relationship will never be good.

14
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,000
It's good that you're confident.

15
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,760
Naturally.

16
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,280
You want the Empress,

17
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,020
and I want His Majesty.

18
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,800
We each take what we need.

19
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,490
What happened today

20
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,170
was purely an accident.

21
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,490
We'll just find another opportunity.

22
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,720
You useless thing.

23
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,160
You can't even come up with a single plan

24
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,560
to deal with the Empress.

25
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,410
Consort Xue.

26
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,600
From today on,

27
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:02,000
you cannot take a single step out of Feixue Palace.

28
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,720
This is your Cold Palace.

29
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,620
Who do you think you are

30
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,960
to confine me?

31
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,220
If you dare take a step out of here,

32
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,200
watch out for yourself and your child.

33
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:20,200
You won't be able to save any of them.

34
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,060
How do you know?

35
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,820
Your Highness.

36
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,880
I didn't.

37
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,360
I didn't say anything.

38
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,000
Since you know I'm pregnant,

39
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,900
and my son brings me honor,

40
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,160
how dare you challenge me?

41
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,320
Whose child it is,

42
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,880
you know perfectly well.

43
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:51,960
You framed me.

44
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,760
I will go to His Majesty

45
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,280
and ask him to punish you.

46
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,690
Don't blame me for not warning you.

47
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,320
Once you go out,

48
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,800
you might end up dead, along with your baby.

49
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,400
Empress,

50
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,740
what exactly do you want to do?

51
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,600
Stay in your Cold Palace.

52
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,690
Stop using these dirty tricks.

53
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,400
You'll only hurt yourself.

54
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,800
I want to see His Majesty.

55
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,279
I'll ask him for justice.

56
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,839
The Imperial Edict arrives!

57
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,959
I wanted to resolve this quickly

58
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,800
and keep Consort Xue here to save her life.

59
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,720
I didn't expect Li Yunxi to cause trouble again.

60
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,480
His Majesty's decree!

61
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,520
The Empress is reasonable,

62
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,040
and acts appropriately.

63
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,480
I second her decision.

64
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,480
Seconded?

65
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,240
Consort Xue.

66
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,100
His Majesty means that

67
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,080
from today on,

68
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:42,440
all harem affairs are up to the Empress.

69
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,200
I want to see His Majesty.

70
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:46,880
I don't believe he would treat me like this.

71
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,040
Consort Xue,

72
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,170
His Majesty says you should behave yourself.

73
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,520
Su Kuang,

74
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,240
what does Li Yunxi mean by this?

75
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,200
You need not worry, Your Highness.

76
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:12,040
His Majesty only wishes for you to do as you please.

77
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,770
As long as you are happy.

78
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,480
Master.

79
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,560
Her Highness suddenly locked Consort Xue up.

80
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,680
I cannot figure out what she intends to do.

81
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,540
She has become suspicious of you.

82
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,560
But I have thought it over again and again,

83
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,890
and I cannot figure out where I slipped up.

84
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,480
Do not act rashly for now.

85
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,330
Just watch and wait.

86
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:38,960
Yes.

87
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,720
Why did you run back from the Palace?

88
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,880
I missed home,

89
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,290
so I wanted to come back for a visit.

90
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,659
Did you make these?

91
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,200
These dishes

92
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,560
were what Mother often cooked when she was alive.

93
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,020
I learned how to make them.

94
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,490
Have a taste.

95
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,640
They are still not as delicious as your mother's.

96
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,000
I just started learning.

97
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,000
I need more encouragement from you.

98
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,560
Haven't seen you for a long time.

99
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:21,480
You've become much more steady.

100
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:23,560
Father.

101
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,040
If you retire from the army one day,

102
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,020
What do you want to do most?

103
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,000
Retire and return home.

104
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,600
I wonder if I'll live to see that day.

105
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,560
You have fought battles all your life.

106
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,320
Why not go to Jiangnan

107
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,840
and live a wealthy, leisurely life?

108
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,560
I'm afraid I can never be idle.

109
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,260
Let me propose a toast.

110
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,840
Did something happen in the Palace?

111
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,280
Everything is fine in the Palace.

112
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,000
Yunxi and I are deeply in love.

113
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,850
Please don't worry.

114
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,920
I will definitely be a

115
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,280
good and dutiful wife.

116
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,560
You drugged the wine.

117
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,409
It is a long way to Jiangnan.

118
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,760
I wish you a safe journey.

119
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,680
If everything goes well,

120
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,600
I will bring Yunxi

121
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,970
to join you and care for you.

122
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,960
When Father wakes up, he will forget everything from the past.

123
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:51,440
I have prepared gold, silver, and valuables in the carriage.

124
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,400
Once you reach Jiangnan,

125
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,760
you can start a new life.

126
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,200
Rest assured, Miss.

127
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,930
I will take good care of Master.

128
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,810
I am leaving now. Take care.

129
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,000
Take care.

130
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,040
Xiao Ling.

131
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,360
You hung the lanterns early.

132
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,240
Did you know tonight

133
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:23,240
would be the night you die?

134
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,520
My life or death

135
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,200
is not up to you.

136
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,780
If I don't avenge them,

137
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,610
I'm unworthy of being their daughter.

138
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,680
Tonight,

139
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,080
I'll send you to hell.

140
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,760
Xie Yan.

141
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,080
If you are a good son,

142
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,039
you should live well.

143
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,679
So you don't fail your parents,

144
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,080
who risked their lives to save you.

145
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,960
Even if I die,

146
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,600
I will avenge my family.

147
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,840
As long as you inhale this Wangyou Smoke,

148
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,160
you can be like Father,

149
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,730
forgetting everything

150
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,330
and starting life anew.

151
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,480
Come here.

152
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,010
Why are you here?

153
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,840
Madam is out on business.

154
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,540
I came to take you home.

155
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:26,600
Yunxi.

156
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,720
I feel both happy

157
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,840
and a little sad.

158
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,240
It's all in the past.

159
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,040
Your Majesty.

160
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,140
Your Highness.

161
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,680
Let us return to the palace.

162
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,880
Leave the cleaning

163
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,940
to the Imperial Guard Bureau.

164
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,760
Let's go home.

165
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:02,880
Let's go home.

166
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,480
How did you know what I came out to do?

167
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:20,650
I looked into the General's situation

168
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,500
and planned to handle it the same way.

169
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,720
We really think alike.

170
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,890
That's what you did before.

171
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,420
I learned from you.

172
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,290
Don't worry.

173
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,240
I've already bought an estate in Jiangnan.

174
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,800
Once the General gets there,

175
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,060
he can live a good life.

176
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,360
You don't need to worry too much.

177
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:46,960
With you here,

178
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,360
I'm not worried about anything.

179
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,200
Li Yunxi,

180
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,200
let's leave here too.

181
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,820
Shall we go to Jiangnan together?

182
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,290
What are you looking at?

183
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,160
I...

184
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,500
I was wondering...

185
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,410
when we will consummate our marriage.

186
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,120
Well...

187
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,040
Well...

188
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:29,160
I...

189
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,560
I...

190
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,160
I... I'm not...

191
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,240
r-ready yet.

192
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,680
D-Don't be afraid.

193
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,250
I'm not that impatient.

194
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,920
That's good.
